Innuos Sense requires you to have an Innuos Music Server with innuOS 2.0 or above connected to your local network.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We keep improving your listening experience through the Innuos Sense app. In this release, we've made the following improvements:

- Improved device information on discovery.
- Improved device discovery algorithm for more consistent results.
- Improved Sense reaction when a device is not available.
- Updated minimum supported Android version for better compatibility.

title: Innuos Sense

creator: Innuos Mobile
descriptionHtml:
Discover your Innuos Servers on the network and access the innuOS UI for managing, exploring and playing your local music, Internet Radio and streaming services.

Innuos Sense requires you to have an Innuos Music Server with innuOS 2.0 or above connected to your local network.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- We've added an option to manually insert the music server's IP address. This is useful for those situations where the home network blocks the app from finding the server.
- Reimplemented network discovery of Innuos Music Servers, which should improve the performance and reliability of this feature.
- We've added a feature where you can open your my.innuos.com links directly in your Sense App.
